    "title": "Ukuaji wa kanisa",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "ukuaji wa kanisa",
    "language": "swh",
    "content": "<p>Kitabu cha Matendo kinaelezea ukuaji wa kanisa baada ya siku ya Pentekoste. Mwanzoni, kanisa liliongezeka kwa idadi. Baada ya Yesu kupaa mbinguni, Wakristo 120 pekee walihudhuria mkutano wa kwanza wa maombi kutafuta mwongozo wa kiungu (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts1:12-Acts1:15\">Matendo 1:12–15</a>). Baada ya Roho Mtakatifu kuwasili kwa nguvu kwenye Pentekoste, idadi ya Wakristo iliongezeka hadi takriban 3,000 (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts2:41\">2:41</a>). Wengi zaidi walikubali mahubiri ya Petro na Yohana kuhusu habari njema za Yesu (injili), na kuongeza idadi hadi takriban 5,000 (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts4:4\">4:4</a>). Kanisa liliendelea kuongezeka (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts5:14\">5:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts6:1\">6:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts9:31\">9:31</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts21:20\">21:20</a>).</p><p>Kuna ushahidi wazi wa kuenea kijiografia (tazama <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts1:8\">Matendo 1:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts9:15\">9:15</a>). Kanisa halikuwepo tu Yerusalemu. Ujumbe wa injili ulienea hadi Lydda, Sharoni, na Yafa kwenye pwani ya Mediterania (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts9:32-Acts9:43\">9:32–43</a>). Ujumbe wa wokovu katika Kristo pia ulipanuka kutoka msingi wake wa Kiyahudi hadi Samaria (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts8:4-Acts8:12\">8:4–12</a>).</p><p>Kisha ikaenea katika Msirofoinike, Kipro, na Antiokia (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts11:19-Acts11:26\">11:19–26</a>). Kama Petro alivyotangaza kwa nyumba ya jemadari Mroma Kornelio, “Mungu haonyeshi upendeleo” (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts10:34\">10:34</a>). Ujumbe wa &quot;injili ya amani kupitia Yesu Kristo&quot; ni kwa kila mtu (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts10:36\">10:36</a>).</p><p>Kama vile imani ya Kikristo ilivyoongezeka kwa idadi na kuenea kijiografia, jamii za Kikristo pia zilipata ukuaji wa kiroho wa kina zaidi. <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts2:42-Acts2:47\">Matendo 2:42–47</a> inaonyesha maendeleo haya katika maisha ya ndani ya kanisa. Inasisitiza maombi ya pamoja wakati wa migogoro, ukarimu katika kushiriki, ujasiri katika mateso, na ushuhuda wa ujasiri (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts4:23-Acts4:31\">4:23–31</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts4:32-Acts4:37\">32–37</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts5:27-Acts5:33\">5:27–33</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts5:40-Acts5:42\">40–42</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts16:19-Acts16:25\">16:19–25</a>). Mahubiri ya shemasi na mwinjilisti Filipo, namna ya kufa kwa shemasi Stefano, na tabia ya mitume Paulo na Sila gerezani zilionyesha ukomavu mkubwa wa kiroho (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts7:59-Acts7:60\">7:59–60</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts8:4-Acts8:40\">8:4–40</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts16:19-Acts16:25\">16:19–25</a>).</p><p>Viongozi wa kanisa waliwahimiza Wakristo, wakawatia moyo katika imani yao, na kuwasaidia kuvumilia mateso (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts14:22\">14:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts15:32\">15:32</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts15:41\">41</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts18:23\">18:23</a>; tazama <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim1:8\">2 Timotheo 1:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim2:1-2Tim2:9\">2:1–9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim3:12\">3:12</a>). Waliishi kwa viwango walivyoweka kwa wengine (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor4:16\">1 Wakorintho 4:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor4:20\">20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil4:9\">Wafilipi 4:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess1:5-1Thess1:8\">1 Wathesalonike 1:5–8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Thess3:9\">2 Wathesalonike 3:9</a>). Ujumuishaji makini wa watu wasio Wayahudi (mataifa) katika kanisa ulisababisha ukuaji muhimu wa kiroho na wa idadi. “Kwa hiyo makanisa yalitiwa nguvu katika imani na yakakua kila siku kwa Hesabu” (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts16:5\">Matendo 16:5</a>).</p><p><u>Sehemu za Kujifunza Zaidi</u></p><p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts1:8\">Matendo 1:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts1:13-Acts1:15\">13–15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts2:41-Acts2:47\">2:41–47</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts4:4\">4:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts4:23-Acts4:37\">23–37</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts5:14\">5:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts5:27-Acts5:33\">27–33</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts5:40-Acts5:42\">40–42</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts6:1\">6:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts7:59\">7:59</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts8:4-Acts8:40\">8:4–40</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts9:15\">9:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts9:31\">31</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts9:35\">35</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts9:42\">42</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts10:34\">10:34</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts10:36\">36</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts11:19-Acts11:26\">11:19–26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts14:22\">14:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts15:32\">15:32</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts15:41\">41</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts16:5\">16:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts16:19-Acts16:25\">19–25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts18:23\">18:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts21:20\">21:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor4:16\">1 Wakorintho 4:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor4:20\">20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil4:9\">Wafilipi 4:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess1:5-1Thess1:8\">1 Wathesalonike 1:5–8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Thess3:9\">2 Wathesalonike 3:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim1:8\">2 Timotheo 1:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim2:1-2Tim2:9\">2:1–9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim3:12\">3:12</a></p>",
